snippet.title: Creating Our First Demo || AggregateCore_Devlog_2
snippet.description:
Hey everyone, we've got another devlog here showcasing a lot of the work we've gotten done over the past couple of months on the game. A demo will be releasing on Steam soon, so subscribe and hit that notification bell if you haven't already! Thanks for watching!

Wishlist On Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2432900/Aggregate_Core/
